'''Zava''' was a [[Mining/Legends|miner]] who was active on the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Vanquo]] in the era of the [[Mandalorian Wars]]. As of the [[Standard year/Legends|year]] [[3964 BBY]], Zava worked at a mining settlement designated [[Outpost 2]] and had a measure of control over the outpost's [[Comm unit/Legends|comm system]]. Zava often enjoyed playing jokes over the comm with another [[Unidentified mining outpost|outpost]] located on a different part of Vanquo. That year, that outpost was sent a false transmission about a [[Mandalorian/Legends|Mandalorian]] invasion in order to clear the area so fugitive former [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Zayne Carrick]] and his friends could scavenge for supplies&mdash;although comm officer [[Zem (miner)|Zem]] initially believed it to be one of Zava's pranks, Carrick [[Mind trick/Legends|mind tricked]] him into believing that a Mandalorian attack was actually occurring.<ref name="kotor7" />

==Behind the scenes==
Zava was mentioned in [[Knights of the Old Republic 7|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 7]], a [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] written by [[John Jackson Miller]] and released in [[2006]].<ref name="kotor7" />

